## data-store package

[TypeORM](https://typeorm.io/) backed plugins. [Agent](./core.agent.md) [plugin](./data-store.datastore.md) that implements [IDataStore](./core.idatastore.md) interface. [Agent](./core.agent.md) [plugin](./data-store.datastoreorm.md) that implements [IDataStoreORM](./data-store.idatastoreorm.md) interface. Provides [KeyStore](./data-store.keystore.md) for [KeyManager](./key-manager.keymanager.md) and [DIDStore](./data-store.didstore.md) for [DIDManager](./did-manager.didmanager.md)
